      "title": "There is no change in the fuel quota this week",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "With the beginning of the third week of August, the release of fuel under the National Fuel License related to this week will start from today (15th).",
        "Although it is spread that there will be a change in the fuel quota given this week, there will be no change in the fuel quota belonging to the fuel license this week as well."
